Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.21,0:00:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在坚定无比的内心里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.02,0:00:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远以最坚强的节奏揭开案情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.02,0:00:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是在山道上小心地开车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.12,0:00:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山谷底散发出案件的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.02,0:00:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.62,0:00:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表似小孩 头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.43,0:00:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.70,0:01:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.41,0:01:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到这么高了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.11,0:01:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还早呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.21,0:01:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才只是一半而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.01,0:02:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.02,0:02:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.52,0:02:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一会儿左转一会儿右转 人都转晕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.03,0:02:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真散漫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.50,0:02:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是叫九十九转岭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.80,0:02:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总共要连续转大小九十九个弯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.20,0:02:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是听就觉得难受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.81,0:02:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.01,0:02:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彦在车里看书呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.32,0:02:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.12,0:02:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到外面来心情会比较舒畅哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.72,0:02:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.32,0:02:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正看到精彩的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.03,0:02:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 说起来灰原这次也没来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.50,0:02:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哀说她有什么事要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.00,0:02:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 她肯定是说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.31,0:03:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如 “我对出游没兴趣 一点也不想去”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.91,0:03:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像真像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.62,0:03:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.32,0:03:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.83,0:03:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.80,0:03:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 快叫警察和救护车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.60,0:03:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.91,0:03:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神山坠车事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.52,0:03:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说你们是在了望台休息的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.32,0:03:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见这辆车摔下来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个后备箱…这么看来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再确认一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.70,0:04:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时没发现有别的可疑的车或者人物是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.30,0:04:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没有发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.11,0:04:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.21,0:04:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.31,0:04:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 警察叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.91,0:04:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 小家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.72,0:04:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以去上边看看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.42,0:04:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 不是小孩看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.02,0:04:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 上边差不多也该完事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.93,0:04:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.33,0:04:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.13,0:04:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要看的话可不能给大家添麻烦哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.41,0:04:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 光彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.11,0:04:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们不去行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.31,0:04:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南那家伙又打算一个人出风头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.02,0:04:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 让他去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.72,0:04:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边有更好的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更好的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.70,0:05:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.90,0:05:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16.33米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.40,0:05:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16.33
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.41,0:05:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.11,0:05:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.51,0:05:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.01,0:05:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 是深蓝色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.52,0:05:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深蓝色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.42,0:05:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.42,0:05:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.43,0:05:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是好不容易出来玩 却碰上这种事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是事故啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.60,0:05:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是事故吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.80,0:05:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 警察不是问你有没有看到别的车吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.31,0:05:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那车是被别的车从后边撞下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.12,0:05:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.42,0:05:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那车的后边很清晰地留着被撞的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.62,0:06:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且上边也发现了另一辆车的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.23,0:06:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且后边那辆车是故意把前边的车撞下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这么说就是杀人事件了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不协助警察没关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.71,0:06:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 反正犯人留下了线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.41,0:06:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是只是一点碎片和撞击后的现场…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.81,0:06:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的警察基本上来说还是比较优秀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.32,0:06:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要分析了碎片的成分和颜色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.22,0:06:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以确定车型 很容易就能找到犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.53,0:06:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.70,0:06:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彦 你说的好东西是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.90,0:06:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.10,0:06:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被柯南听到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.11,0:06:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个 元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.61,0:06:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.11,0:07:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是暗号啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.52,0:07:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.22,0:07:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.02,0:07:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是从刚才事故现场的车下边发现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.83,0:07:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 不告诉警察叔叔没关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.13,0:07:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是刚才的只是坠落事故啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.30,0:07:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会想到和暗号有关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.00,0:07:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 说到暗号就让人想到藏宝的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.41,0:07:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.21,0:07:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝藏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后仔细看这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.21,0:07:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最上面的框里写着100-1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.12,0:07:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 100减1等于多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.52,0:07:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是99…99…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.03,0:07:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,99
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.83,0:07:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.60,0:07:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么元太 从99你能联想到什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.10,0:07:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,99…99…99…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.81,0:07:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救护车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.81,0:08:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这里怎么会跑出来救护车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.62,0:08:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是九九乘法口诀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.62,0:08:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.32,0:08:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指九十九转岭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.12,0:08:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才博士也说了有九十九个转弯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.73,0:08:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.53,0:08:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这个暗号应该是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.40,0:08:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表示九十九转岭的某个场所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.70,0:08:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经明白了吗 光彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.00,0:08:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有 但是总觉得这暗号以前在哪里见过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.41,0:08:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里见过呢 光彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.51,0:08:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们几个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.21,0:08:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始就嘀咕什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.82,0:08:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.32,0:08:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 没有暗号什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.02,0:08:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.22,0:08:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是刚才看的小说里的暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.73,0:08:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于柯南你来说太简单了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.20,0:08:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 小孩的玩意儿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.50,0:09:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.01,0:09:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就和博士钓鱼去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.41,0:09:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要好好地劈柴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.02,0:09:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.62,0:09:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.42,0:09:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彦 真的明白了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.43,0:09:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才读的书里出现过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.73,0:09:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.30,0:09:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.10,0:09:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电脑的键盘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.90,0:09:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.40,0:09:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从左上角开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.01,0:09:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一个数字都对应一个假名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.91,0:09:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如14是た 27就是と
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.11,0:09:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.12,0:09:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们来试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.22,0:09:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 你来念暗号的数字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.02,0:09:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.52,0:09:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,04 23 38
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.83,0:10:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,04是う 23是せ 38是つ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.00,0:10:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うせつ（右转）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.10,0:10:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这个符号是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.51,0:10:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是道路的形状呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.01,0:10:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 一定是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.41,0:10:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以第一句暗号的意思就是 “十字路口右转”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.32,0:10:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彦好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.02,0:10:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.02,0:10:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来写
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.70,0:10:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不上钩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.90,0:10:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.30,0:10:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请读一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.80,0:10:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看地图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.51,0:10:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了九十九转岭之后 十字路口往右转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.01,0:10:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T字路口往右转 下一个十字路口左转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.41,0:10:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了两座桥 接着右转就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.52,0:10:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 就是这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.32,0:11:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这个表示这里的话 那么相当近呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.23,0:11:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.03,0:11:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会发现宝藏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.00,0:11:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南一定会很懊恼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.71,0:11:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们在二楼吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.41,0:11:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上去找了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.22,0:11:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.72,0:11:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么地方都找不到孩子们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.73,0:11:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.90,0:11:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 光彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.21,0:11:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.01,0:11:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩一点就到了 坚持啊 元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是在第二座桥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.12,0:12:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个路口右转之后就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.02,0:12:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那么远啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.22,0:12:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.22,0:12:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到宝藏的话就能吃鳗鱼饭了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.13,0:12:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳗鱼饭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.00,0:12:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 找到宝藏以后就要吃鳗鱼饭吃到肚子涨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.90,0:12:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧光彦 鳗鱼饭100万份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.30,0:12:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是这股劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.31,0:12:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 这个也许是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.91,0:12:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现什么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.21,0:12:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 立刻给警察打电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.92,0:12:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.92,0:12:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们几个现在正在往刚才事故的犯人那走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.22,0:12:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.02,0:12:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才他们在车里说的就是这个东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.53,0:12:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.41,0:13:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了 就是那里 元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.01,0:13:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彦 真的是这里没错吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.72,0:13:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不像是有宝藏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.52,0:13:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.22,0:13:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是按照暗号说的路线来的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.83,0:13:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝藏就是藏在这种意外的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.00,0:13:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 进去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.81,0:13:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.71,0:13:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察立刻就会去搜查那里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.12,0:13:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们也赶紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.02,0:13:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.52,0:13:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没有人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.22,0:13:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 光彦 哪里有宝藏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.80,0:14:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最里面的建筑物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.30,0:14:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看 只有那栋建筑物上着锁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.61,0:14:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.01,0:14:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.82,0:14:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.92,0:14:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.80,0:14:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是进口车啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.80,0:14:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 光彦 哪里都没有宝藏的影子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.71,0:14:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.31,0:14:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些车很可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.01,0:14:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 都没有牌照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.72,0:14:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.02,0:14:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 光彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.02,0:14:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.62,0:14:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些可能是被盗的车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.03,0:15:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是打算卖到外国去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.10,0:15:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们到了偷车贼的老窝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.01,0:15:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是事故现场的小孩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.62,0:15:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胡子老头和另外一个小孩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.03,0:15:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放老实点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.00,0:15:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.80,0:15:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是枪声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.80,0:15:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.00,0:15:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 开快一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.80,0:15:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.61,0:15:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再问一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.21,0:15:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胡子老头和另外一个小孩哪儿去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.22,0:15:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.32,0:15:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.12,0:16:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.62,0:16:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能说 是咱们自己擅自跑出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.93,0:16:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能连累柯南他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.50,0:16:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.50,0:16:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你们是想死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.71,0:16:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.11,0:16:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 这次只有5辆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.02,0:16:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤那小子害怕了 开了一辆跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.02,0:16:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.62,0:16:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经解决掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.53,0:16:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从后边把他撞下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.00,0:16:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.30,0:16:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在出事之前解决问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.20,0:16:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都消灭了就没有证据了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.11,0:16:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.42,0:17:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.02,0:17:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎么样 拿枪指着小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.32,0:17:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.52,0:17:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是事故现场的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.23,0:17:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 省得我找了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.83,0:17:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.80,0:17:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听吧 听见了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.50,0:17:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警车的警笛声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.60,0:17:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.90,0:17:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来这里的哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.21,0:17:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来逮捕叔叔你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.01,0:17:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.01,0:17:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.02,0:17:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 警察先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.62,0:17:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这么多人来有什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.62,0:17:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在谈这个之前 不打算把枪给我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.03,0:17:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说它吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.53,0:17:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这帮小孩私自闯进这里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.80,0:17:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是吓吓他们而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.20,0:17:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 那边的车是你的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.21,0:18:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啊 怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.01,0:18:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.41,0:18:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九十九转岭发生了汽车落崖事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.82,0:18:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都像是跟你的车相撞之后摔下去的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.22,0:18:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你这车好像也在哪里撞过似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.12,0:18:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你们是怀疑我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.43,0:18:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟它一样的车至少有几百辆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.40,0:18:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为其中有几辆会在那个时候出现在附近呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时你在什么地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.71,0:18:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 那只是事故而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.21,0:18:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我只顾欣赏风景没注意…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.71,0:18:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等发现的时候已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.82,0:18:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察叔叔 他在胡说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.42,0:18:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吵 小孩闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.52,0:18:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才打电话时候明明说是撞下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.83,0:18:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也听到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.53,0:18:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.13,0:18:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 警察先生 这样的小孩的话能相信吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.00,0:19:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那种急转弯的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.40,0:19:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意相撞的可能性简直就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.91,0:19:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你就做得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.61,0:19:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭老头 少在那里胡说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.91,0:19:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有证据吗 证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.91,0:19:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然有证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.02,0:19:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被撞下去的车总共留下了两条刹车痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.33,0:19:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说你总共撞了它两次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.50,0:19:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样 一次没停住又撞了一下而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能说没有这种可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.71,0:19:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两条刹车痕之间的距离测量了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.21,0:19:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是16.33米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.61,0:19:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又是以多少时速在那条路上行驶的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.52,0:19:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概30公里左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.52,0:19:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.33,0:20:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时速30公里的话也就是大概8.3米/秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.50,0:20:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说16.33米除以8.3米/秒 结果约为2秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.51,0:20:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说在第一次相撞之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.31,0:20:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有减速也没有刹车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.42,0:20:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是又一次和它相撞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.02,0:20:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是故意的话又是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.32,0:20:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么想解释的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.33,0:20:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们到局里慢慢解释吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.20,0:20:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.30,0:20:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.20,0:20:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面的仓库里有很多没有牌照的高级车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.50,0:20:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是被盗的车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.71,0:20:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们帮了大忙了 小家伙们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.11,0:20:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以记住了 以后不许再做这种危险的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.42,0:20:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.32,0:22:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 真难劈开啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.12,0:22:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 柴不够了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.03,0:22:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.73,0:22:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也稍微来帮一下忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.60,0:22:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.50,0:22:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为你们自己到处乱跑才会变成现在这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.40,0:22:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.01,0:22:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“是” 说一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.61,0:23:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.01,0:23:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这样擅自行动是很危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.62,0:23:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还是吃惊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.42,0:23:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.72,0:23:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为柯南一下子就读懂暗号了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.02,0:23:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彦也很厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.23,0:23:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是暗号 面对枪口的时候也毫不畏惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.10,0:23:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是正好书里出现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.00,0:23:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊 我也读来试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.40,0:23:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 正好有适合元太读的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.91,0:23:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫《小孩子难办的杀人事件》
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.91,0:23:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是读和你一样的好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.62,0:23:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是在反省吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.42,0:23:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里好有沉静的美感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.12,0:23:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才叫真正的享受呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.73,0:23:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 她在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.83,0:23:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么鬼鬼祟祟的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.20,0:23:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说大师是因为害怕那个魔物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.30,0:24:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个池塘真有什么魔物吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.50,0:24:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.71,0:24:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大师他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.61,0:24:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.11,0:24:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五彩传说这水御殿（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.32,0:24:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.92,0:24:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂轴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.72,0:24:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次是难懂的动画原创
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.52,0:24:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看几遍也不明白为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.80,0:00:07.15,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场恋爱令人战栗，震惊，焦虑难耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.40,0:00:10.75,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不可名状的力量驱使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:18.35,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来势汹涌让人无法禁闭心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.45,0:00:36.40,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们感受得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.95,0:00:47.05,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱情的利刺或许同样加之于你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.15,0:00:53.55,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知你究竟为何心痛 为何胆怯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.70,0:00:58.15,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕去面对纠葛不清的二人真实面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.25,0:01:01.65,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生怕面对彼此的事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.50,0:01:07.05,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场恋爱令人战栗，震惊，焦虑难耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.15,0:01:14.30,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使迷茫想时似乎随着清风而逝 仍然无法抱个满怀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.40,0:01:17.75,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我小小的胸臆中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.90,0:01:21.37,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法紧闭心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.47,0:01:25.95,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深藏着朝着下一步迈进的惶惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.00,0:01:35.35,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,500)}即使我已将迷惑拥个满怀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.20,0:21:23.40,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透过窗户看到天空 描绘着飞机留下的云迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.40,0:21:31.80,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,净是回想今天和你争吵的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.30,0:21:42.45,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琐碎的事情弄得束手无策 坐立不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.45,0:21:47.00,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不自然地马上给你打电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.10,0:21:50.60,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是喜欢看到你迷人的笑脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.00,0:21:55.95,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常幸福的时光将要来临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.05,0:22:01.10,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴随着痛苦的脚步声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.20,0:22:09.95,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过于多心反而陷入更深的困境 然而却又守侯在你的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.00,0:22:18.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏之幻想 合上双眼最先浮现眼前的还是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.40,0:22:23.20,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别无所求 只想和你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.30,0:22:28.45,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算束手无策也愿意 紧牵的手永不放开
